Description:
    en: Generate a layout using the ERGO Insurance Group's style. You can customize it or add your own as well.
    it: Crea un layout secondo lo stile del gruppo assicurativo ERGO. Puoi personalizzarlo o aggiungerti il tuo.

Rails version supported:
    3.1

Available layout:
    ergo [default]

Example:
    rails generate ergolay
    rails generate ergolay --main_color=#c8c8c8
    rails generate ergolay layout1 --main_color=rgb(200,150,200) --second-color=yellow
    rails generate ergolay layout2 --skip-pagination --skip-authentication --skip-authorization

This will create:
    config/initializers/config.rb
    app/assets/stylesheets/ergo.sass
    app/helpers/layout_helper.rb
    app/views/layouts/application.html.erb
    app/views/layouts/_ergo.html.erb
    app/views/application/_message.html.erb
    app/views/application/_session.html.erb
    config/locales/en.yml
    config/locales/it.yml
    config/locales/kaminari.en.yml
    config/locales/kaminari.it.yml
    app/views/layouts/kaminari/_next_page.html.erb
    app/views/layouts/kaminari/_page.html.erb
    app/views/layouts/kaminari/_paginator.html.erb
    app/views/layouts/kaminari/_prev_page.html.erb
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/kaminari/ergo_nav.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/bg_but_gray.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/bg_top.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ergo_200.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ergo_button_170_126.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ergo_button_229_170.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ico_back.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ico_next.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ico_v.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/ico_x.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/input_background_bn.png
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/msg_error.gif
    app/assets/images/styles/ergo/msg_notice.gif
